<body><div><span><strong>Article Title:</strong> </span><span>Simple Ways to Earn Money Every Day</span></div><br />
<div><span><strong>Article Content: </strong></span><br /><span><p>You’re short on cash, rent’s due, and your next payday is still six days away. Before you head to the nearest pawn shop, check out these simple ways to earn more money. There’s a good chance that you could be getting paid for things that you already do every day.</p>
<h2>Try Your Luck with Sweepstakes</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4058/4673226222_cebf2c9f4c.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="375" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/brizo_the_scot/" target="_blank">B4bees</a></p>
<p>The Internet is loaded with contests and sweepstakes offers. From high dollar cash drawings and gift cards to sophisticated electronics and baby gear, there are hundreds of prizes just waiting to be won. Remember, the more you enter, the better your chances of winning. You can always sell items you don’t need!</p>
<h2>Do Some Virtual Coupon Clipping</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4012/4650502892_87d33bbc87.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="334" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/misscrabette/" target="_blank">misscrabette</a></p>
<p>As if it isn’t enough to save money on the products and services you need, there are some websites that reward you with points or other perks every time you use one of their coupons. You can find <a href="http://coupons.rewardit.com/professional-services/" target="_blank">professional service coupons</a> for carpet cleaning, dog grooming, haircuts, and much more, as well as coupons for groceries and other necessities.</p>
<h2>Bring Some Mystery into Your Life</h2>
<p><img src="http://secretwebshopper.org/items/mystery_shopping.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="357" /></p>
<p>Image via <a href="http://secretwebshopper.org/items/mystery_shopping.jpg" target="_blank">SecretWebShopper</a></p>
<p>There are dozens of <a href="http://ezinearticles.com/?Secret-Shopper-Compensation&id=410716">mystery shopper</a> jobs available. These positions may include visiting stores, restaurants, or even financial institutions. Participants are typically compensated for their purchases, in addition to their time so it’s an excellent way to make extra money doing things you normally spend money to do.</p>
<h2>Make Money for the Things You Buy</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm5.staticflickr.com/4017/4241390495_635818a2b6.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="302" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/zooboing/" target="_blank">Patrick Hoesly</a></p>
<p>You don’t have to use coupons or become a mystery shopper to earn money when you make purchases. Simply sign up with a site that has a cash back program, shop at your favorite online stores through the website’s links, and collect points that can be redeemed for cash. <a href="http://coupons.rewardit.com/professional-services/" target="_blank">Using cash rewards for purchases</a> is like winning a shopping spree!</p>
<h2>Get Paid for Surfing the Web</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3606/3436921886_e0906c6f6c.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="332" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/larryvincent/" target="_blank">larryvincent</a></p>
<p>Another great way to earn money doing something you already do, without pay, every day. Take the time to find a website that not only pays you to surf, but also has other income earning options, such as cash back rewards, coupons, or sweepstakes. Paid surfing programs can put money in your pocket quickly as long as you follow the rules.</p>
<h2>Answer a Few Questions</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm1.staticflickr.com/129/376588066_ae1f1f8363.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="500" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/xurble/" target="_blank">Xurble</a></p>
<p>Many people earn a sizable second income completing online surveys in their spare time. The best <a href="http://frugalliving.about.com/od/moneymanagement/p/Online_Surveys.htm">paid survey sites</a> are free to join, and offer a variety of interesting questionnaires based on your habits and interests. Some opportunities offer cash compensation, but many reward their participants with points or sweepstakes entries.</p>
<h2>Share Your Knowledge</h2>
<p><img src="http://farm2.staticflickr.com/1351/1184491822_7faf8c78dc.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="375" /></p>
<p>Flickr by <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/11777427@N05/">Doctor Panelstein</a></p>
<p>From relationship dilemmas to science questions, many sites will pay you to answer questions and give advice on topics you enjoy. There are also websites that reward individuals for submitting reviews of products and businesses that they have used personally. If you have your own blog, there are companies that will offer reasonable compensation if you advertise or review their products.</p>
<p>Who couldn’t use some extra cash? Especially when you can easily earn money every day doing things you enjoy. Just a few of the ideas above can bring in the extra money you need with hardly any effort!</p>
